        "translations": {
          "en": "My father (may God be pleased with him) narrated to us, he said: Ali ibn Ibrahim ibn Hashim narrated to us from his father Ibrahim ibn Hashim, he said: Ibrahim ibn Raja' al-Jahdari narrated to me, he said: Waki' ibn al-Jarrah narrated to us from Sharik ibn Abdullah, from Abdullah ibn Muhammad ibn Aqil, from Jabir ibn Abdullah al-Ansari, who said: The Messenger of God (may God bless him and his family) said:",
